eu.focusnet.app.util

Class Constant.Navigation

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.focusnet.app.util.Constant.Navigation
  • Enclosing class:
    Constant

    public static final class Constant.Navigation
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants related to the navigation system of our application. All Projects, Dashboards & Tools (Pages) and widgets are uniquely identified by a path within the application, and these constants define the format of this path.

    The different list item types and constants used for referencing specific menu entries are also defined here.
